layout(bytes32).details: "Binds" this struct to a storage slot.

params.slot_: The first slot to use in the range of slots used by the struct.

returns.layout_: A struct from a Layout library bound to the provided slot.

slot(ERC20BaseStruct storage).details: Provides the storage pointer bound to a Struct instance.
